N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4231.8 - Deposit may be forfeited

State Regulations

Before considering an objection the judges may require a
deposit of $25, which shall be forfeited if the objection is decided to be
frivolous or vexatious. Notes
